Prohibited periods: Strictly prohibited before rapeseed 2-leaf stage and during bolting, effectiveness is poor at low temperatures (<8°C) and can easily damage seedlings.
Dosage and method:
Cabbage-type rapeseed: Use 20-30ml of 24% Sethoxydim emulsifiable concentrate per mu, mix with 30kg of water for stem and leaf spray;
Chinese cabbage-type / Mustard-type rapeseed: Use 15-20ml per mu, first test in a small area, expand only if no phytotoxicity is observed.

